      <h1>TEARS</h1>

      <h4>Tears they are,<br>
So I was told,<br>
Why they have to come,<br>
That I do not know <br>
Will they dry one day? <br>
Maybe when I grow old.</h4>
  <h5> - Busari Azeezat</h5>

